 own qualifying examples include \"the April 2024 closure of Iran's western airspace.\" The current event — closure of all airports in the west part of Tehran FIR — is structurally comparable to that qualifying example.\n- The rule explicitly contemplates that \"exceptions for certain flights pre-approved by the Iranian Civil Aviation Authority\" do not disqualify a broad closure. The NOTAM's permission regime is precisely this kind of exception.\n- \"ALL AIRPORTS IN WEST PART OF TEHRAN FIR ARE CLSD\" is a broad, region-wide measure. Closing all airports in a region effectively suspends commercial arrivals and departures across that region. The exceptions are enumerated, daylight-only, and require fresh individual CAA approval — these are exactly the \"limited exceptions\" the rule contemplates.\n- The Indian Express describes this as Iran closing \"the airspace over its western half\" and \"suspending all civil flight permits in the western sector.\" Credible reporting treats this as a regional closure.\n\nThe defendant's strongest point is that the NOTAM is categorized as \"AD Airport Operations\" rather than explicitly an airspace/overflight ban. But the market rule does not require an explicit overflight prohibition — it covers \"commercial flights transiting, arriving in, and departing from\" a major region. Closing all airports in a region with only narrow exceptions directly impacts arrivals and departures across that region. The rule's own cited qualifying example (April 2024 western airspace closure) was described similarly.\n\nUnder **preponderance of the evidence** — more likely than not — the record establishes that Iran broadly closed airport operations across the western Tehran FIR, a major Iranian airspace region, with only limited CAA-controlled daylight exceptions, for non-weather reasons, effective through the deadline. This fits the major-region path.\n\nI'm ready to vote."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_015E4pR9TpQneE6Qj5tRoCYE","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"anthropic/claude-opus-4.6-fast","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781914216015,"responseId":"gen-1781914216-MAWn8sj9Ssz0ChTPkjX0","responseModel":"anthropic/claude-4.6-opus-fast-20260407"}}
